description: Erection of 6 blocks comprising 3 - 7 storeys to provide a total of 90 residential units (3 x 6 bed, 1x 4 bed, 15 x 3 bed, 41 x 2 bed and 30 x 1 bed) plus 25 car parking spaces(including 3 wheelchair accessible and a disabled car port), 54 cycle sheds, bin stores/recycling areas. New vehicular access and exit with automatic gates and pedestrain access with gates and landscaping with children's play area.
